Which of the following best describes brassinosteroids' effect on root growth at low and high concentrations respectively?

choices.W: Low concentrations inhibit root growth, High concentrations promote root growth
choices.X: Low concentrations promote root growth, High concentrations inhibit root growth
choices.Y: Both low and high concentrations inhibit root growth
choices.Z: Both low and high concentrations promote root growth

answer: X) LOW CONCENTRATIONS PROMOTE ROOT GROWTH, HIGH CONCENTRATIONS INHIBIT ROOT GROWTH
